high_descs: turn right and walk to the toilet at the end of the room, then turn left to walk to the towel rack
grab the spray bottle off of the towel rack
turn around and walk to the toilet ahead
place the spray bottle on top of the toilet
turn around and walk to the towel rack again
grab the spray bottle off of the towel rack
turn around and walk to the toilet up ahead
place the spray bottle on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: place two spray bottles on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk across the room, then turn to the left and walk across the room.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle that is closest to the blue trash bin.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Put the yellow spray bottle on top of the toilet.
Turn around and walk across the room then look up.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle on the bottom shelf.
Turn around and walk to the toilet then look up.
Put the yellow spray bottle on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put away the yellow spray bottles.

high_descs: Walk to the bathroom shelf on your right.
Grab a spray bottle from the shelf.
Turn behind you to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the toilet.
Go back to the bathroom shelf behind you.
Grab another spray bottle from the shelf.
Walk to the toilet behind you.
Put the spray bottle on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move spray bottles from the shelf to the toilet.
